WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
What if you could use genetic engineering to stop humanity's most dangerous predator?

00:07.000 --> 00:11.820
The deadliest animal on the planet responsible for the death of billions,

00:11.820 --> 00:17.800
the mighty mosquito. Along with other diseases, it plays host to malaria,

00:17.800 --> 00:23.120
one of the cruelest parasites on Earth, possibly the single biggest killer of humans in history.

00:23.120 --> 00:29.040
In 2015 alone, hundreds of millions were infected and almost half a million people died.

00:29.040 --> 00:34.780
