Malaria is caused by a group of microorganisms, plasmodia. Very weird microorganisms that consist

01:05.160 --> 01:11.720
of just a single cell. They're parasites that completely rely on mosquitoes. Malaria always

01:11.720 --> 01:17.280
starts with an insect bite. In its salivary glands, thousands of sporozoites wait until

01:17.280 --> 01:22.280
